<title>The Story of Africa| BBC World Service</title>
<!--BBC World Service:International news, analysis and information in English and 42 other languages--> 
<META Name="description" Content="The history of the continent from an African perspective. With hundreds of pages, and multi-media,  the BBC investigates the events and characters that have made African history from the origins of humankind to the end of South African apartheid.">
